pd_0_com_0text: Woah! Finally we are free! Listen, before we wander off, we'd like to offer you our help in your quest. I know it sounds harsh, but both Red and Yellow wouldn't really be of any help...
pd_2_com_0text: I'm afraid I did not clarify your position clearly. You have to choose between me, a fine historian, and that ever-talking charlatan of my blue friend.
pd_3_com_0text: That's the spirit my friend! I know a lot of good jokes about the undeads. You know, I once was the joker of a litch court. Everyone literally DIED of laughs.
pd_4_com_0text: So, I have to choose between one of you two, right?
pd_5_com_0text: You are correct, indeed. I shall offer all my knowledge about history and architecture: with me as a guide, this place will have no secrets for you.
pd_6_com_0text: What about you joker, what can you offer me?
pd_7_com_0text: Well, with me you will never be alone. I always know how to lighten up the mood with some stories and jokes. The adventurer life can very hard, you'll need someone to cheer you up fromtime to time.
pd_8_com_0text: I'll choose the historian. I'd like to know more about this place.
pd_8_com_1text: I'll choose the joker. Nothing is better than a good chat while adventuring.
pd_9_com_0text: A fine choice indeed. You may call me Sir Gilbert. I am pleased to be your guide.
pd_10_com_0text: I'm Jasper! You chose me, Of CORPSE you did! The funniest talking ghost head is at your service.
